DC LED font converter

This small tool helps creating a font file for the dcled project.

This prject can be found at
http://www.last-outpost.com/~malakai/dcled/

To convert the existing font to a png copy the content from the dcled.c to a
TXT-file. Then run

php font_convert.php -i txt -f your_txt_file.txt -o png -F font.png

Then use any graphics editor to edit the font.png and afterwards run

php font_convert.php -i png -f png -o txt -F new_font.txt

and copy the content into the initfont1 function and recompile the dcled
project.